# Loaded by Expo for local dev (`EXPO_PUBLIC_*` must be prefixed).
# Copy to `.env.development` and tweak, then restart `npx expo start`.

# Omit this entirely in dev → the app guesses the Metro host + `:8787` (see `lib/api.ts`).
# EXPLICIT overrides (tunnel / custom port):

# Same machine + iOS Simulator / web:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8787

# Physical device → Mac LAN IP:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.x.x:8787
